==== ENTRY 2 ====
HEADWORD: Melodize
<hw>Mel"o*dize</hw>, <pos>v. i.</pos> <def>To make melody; to compose
melodies; to harmonize.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Melodrama</ent>⟦br⟧
